<P>
DEMONSTRATIONS -- SOUTH AFRICA; APARTHEID; DISSIDENTS -- SOUTH AFRICA; BLACKS 
-- SOUTH AFRICA; CIVIL DISOBEDIENCE; RACIAL RELATIONS -- SOUTH AFRICA 
</P>
